casebody.data:
GREEN v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 18,

September Term, 1960.]

Decided October 13, 1960.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For the reasons stated by Judge Manley for dismissing the petition, the application for leave to appeal is denied.

Application denied.
